content.rendered:
“I would love to work on being able to walk my dog without him being so afraid, pulling, and barking. I would say this is my highest priority. I am currently unable to work outside of the home because he has never learned to be away from me (he was a puppy in pandemic). I cannot be away for more than 2hrs before he starts crying.

I would love to be able to leave the house for longer periods of time and hopefully be able to get a job outside the home. I would say this is my second top priority. I would also like to be able to have people over to my house with mooshi not jumping all over them. I would also love it if I could get him to stop barking at the door. “

We also talked on the phone on some tips about carting.
